|<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.WmiConfigurationAttribute.NamespaceSecurity>|<span data-ttu-id="24627-109">層使用的命名空間安全性 (DACL)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="24627-109">-   The security (DACL) on the namespace used.</span></span>|  
